Git Commit Aliases

Helpers for creating commits.

$ [prgm]git wip[/prgm]                  # Commit with "wip" message (skips hooks)
$ [prgm]git amend[/prgm]                # Edit the last commit message

[prgm]wip[/prgm] is useful for quick work-in-progress commits. Uses [arg]--no-verify[/arg] to skip pre-commit hooks.
